:GRAPH EZ607b
:TITLE Debt Crisis
:X-AXIS Time
:X-DIV 10
:Y-DIV 3
:X-MIN 0
:SCALE
:VAR production plants
:UNITS $
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 300
:LINE-WIDTH 4
:VAR debt
:UNITS $
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 300
:LINE-WIDTH 3
:VAR profit
:UNITS $
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 300
:LINE-WIDTH 2

:GRAPH EZ607c
:TITLE Debt Crisis
:X-AXIS Time
:X-DIV 10
:X-MIN 0
:SCALE
:VAR debt
:Y-MIN 0
:Y-MAX 2000
:DATASET credit = 50
:LINE-WIDTH 1
:VAR debt
:DATASET credit = 60
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR debt
:DATASET credit = 70
:LINE-WIDTH 3
:VAR debt
:DATASET credit = 80
:LINE-WIDTH 4
:VAR debt
